Martell kicked off their new series Martell HOME LIVE a talk show dedicated to bold ideas and conversations which hosted some of the biggest names in hip hop including Nigeria’s very own M.I Abaga. In a room adorned with cocktails, spirited energy and a warm atmosphere, the host for the evening, Killer Mike, began the first episode by welcoming everyone in attendance and at home watching live via a YouTube livestream.
The evening blossomed into an intimate night full of by performances and discussions featuring Princess Nokia and Big Freedia alongside the Atlanta rapper. The talk show celebrated people who use their platforms to push boundaries and challenge norms, while daring to leave a lasting legacy that inspires others to do the same. Watch “Martell Home Live” Via YouTube below; 